  "Description": {
    "English": "Ancient words are carved into this <span class=\"name name-stellar\">living document</span>. They read:<br><br>'The worm lord towers above the dusty earth; its flesh becomes the sky.<br>Our pathetic shells cannot follow, cannot reach its height, cannot reach its depths.<br>We offer ourselves to the ground.<br>We beg our sacrifice accepted.'",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "这份<span class=\"name name-stellar\">活经文</span>上刻着古老的文字。上面写道：<br><br>“蠕虫领主的身影徘徊于尘土之上，躯体则化为了天空。<br>吾等肉体凡胎无法追随，无法到达那种高度，更无法触及那渊底。<br>吾等将自身献给大地。<br>吾等乞求自我的牺牲能被接受。”",
    "TraditionalChinese": "被刻進<span class=\"name name-stellar\">活體文件</span>的古老文字。上頭刻著：<br><br>「蟲王佇立在沙土之上，其血肉遮天。<br>我們可憐的軀殼無可企及其高度與深度。<br>我們匍匐於土地，奉獻出自身。<br>我們乞求自身奉獻能獲得接納。」"
  },
